{
  "stem": "7094.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I then became employed by Hitlerjugend, because this was run by Hitlerjugend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I started by-- you know, there were six other German girls, and I started, uh, being the, uh-- the lowest in the grade and coal into-- they didn't have central heating, but they had these ovens-- carrying coal.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But eventually I graduated, and I become the chief cook.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that was, uh, just one of those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, cleaning-- mostly cleaning, washing, going to the bakery, because also we cooked, but baking for the weekend.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took it to the bakery, to the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a little bit outside town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there again came another difficulty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whereas in Berlin you had a special arbeitsamt-- sort of a-- not 'arbeitsamt'-- embassy-- Ukrainian-- here the local police-- and this is where I have the document that I will show you.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That once I got, uh, a letter, soon after I arrived, that I have to register in the local police.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I-- unsuspectingly-- I went to the local police and produced my documents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By that time, I had the [INAUDIBLE] documents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he looked at it, and he said, oh, you will be very pleased, because there is a boy from [INAUDIBLE]-- you know, this little village with Olga Demczyzszak.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He is here, and he is working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you will be very pleased to have a landsman with you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I died at that moment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought to myself, what am I doing?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How-- but there was nothing-- I didn't have freedom to travel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't leave this position to go somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to stay put.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Being outside the town, I didn't venture very much into the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
